  "body": "I've run a few tests in our stage environment, and for the most part things work great.\r\n\r\nHowever, I noticed that when the schema swap workflow is propagating backups it takes down the replica node without promoting another node to replica.\r\n\r\nWhen semi-sync is enabled this causes a write lock on the master because rdonly nodes do NOT ack the master for semi-sync.\r\n\r\nI think we should promote a rdonly node to a replica while we are updating the old replica.",
